functions.name: delegate
functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.

msg.content: From which countries do the people who completed an EGOT over a span greater than 40 years come from?
From which countries do the people who completed an EGOT over a span greater than 40 years come from?

I was not able to find any people who completed an EGOT over a span greater than 40 years.

Tim Rice achieved his EGOT over a span of 37 years, from 1980 to 2018. He is from the United Kingdom.

John Gielgud achieved his EGOT over a span of 38 years, from 1948 to 1986. He was born in South Kensington, London, which is part of the United Kingdom.

Jonathan Tunick achieved his EGOT in 38 years, from 1977 to 2015. Tunick was born in New Jersey, USA, and studied at the Juilliard School in New York.

Did you want to know more about EGOT winners?
